18 Section 8. Section 7-14-210, MCA, is amended to read:
19 "7-14-210. Election on question of creating urban transportation district or addition to district.
20 (1) The commissioners, on completion of the public hearing required by 7-14-203(1) or 7-14-207, shall proceed
21 by resolution to refer the creation of the district or an addition to a district to the persons qualified to vote on the
22 proposition.
23 (2) The election must be held in accordance with Title 13, chapter 1, part 5."
